219
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:40,570
Bawa saya ke Api Roh.

220
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,690
Atas mayat saya.

221
00:14:44,920 --> 00:14:45,920
Dalam kes itu...

222
00:15:49,870 --> 00:15:52,900
